dct_title_s: Map of Khorasan, and neighbouring countries illustrating the paper by Lieut. Colonel C. E. Stewart, 5th Punjab Infantry
dct_description_sm: Stewart's route shown in red. Persian boundary with Afghanistan and Turkmen territory is shown. Routes and distances between cities are shown. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Karakum Desert shown by shading. From: Proceedings of the Royal Geographical Society and monthly record of geography. Vol. 3 (1881), no. 9, pp. 513-46; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6873
